snippet.title: Jumpy Jumptime itch.IO Early Access Release Trailer - Unreal Engine 5 Indie Game
snippet.description:
Hey!
I thought I would create a small release trailer for yesterday's release of Jumpy on the itch.io platform. I actually find the idea quite funny. How do you like it?

Buy Jumpy Jumptime here:
https://jumpyjumptime.itch.io/jumpy-jumptime

You can also wishlist it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2824170/Jumpy_Jumptime/
